        <text>
          <content>
            <paragraph align="center">○壬戌/獻納<index num="1566074_0" ref="M_0003158" sort="K" type="이름">申靖夏</index>疏論:</paragraph>
            <paragraph align="center">
              <quotation>湖西左道京試官<index num="1566075_0" ref="M_0062938" sort="K" type="이름">金有慶</index>, 不由直路, 拕過家鄕, 盤桓郡邑, 淹延時日。 湖中士風偸薄, 每疑考官行私, 而<index num="1566076_0" ref="M_0062938" sort="K" type="이름">有慶</index>作事謬妄, 乃至於此。 宜趁未開場前拿推, 以嚴科場。</quotation>
            </paragraph>
            <paragraph align="center">從之, 代送他試官。</paragraph>
          </content>
        </text>
